Package jdk.jpackage.internal.model

package jdk.jpackage.internal.model
Classes and interfaces of the internal application packaging model. Primary entities are: Application, Package, and Launcher.
API Note:
All methods of all interfaces and classes in this package return non-null values unless stated otherwise.
